name: Alternative Lynels [Maned]
desc: Adds 5 new Lynels to your game, one for each type of Lynel. Each Lynel is redesigned with a different style of horns but still with their manes. Red maned Lynel, Blue maned Lynel, white maned Lynel, Silver maned Lynel and Gold maned Lynel all got changed in a unique way and different from one another while still being recognizable from their own base type.
